changeset:   2026:6711ac5e6fe3
user:        Trevor Williams <phase1geo@users.sourceforge.net>
date:        Sat Apr 02 23:46:23 2016 -0500
files:       lib/folding.tcl lib/version.tcl lib/vim.tcl
description:
* Adding 'zA' Vim command support (toggle all deeply).
* Adding 'foldenable' Vim option support (folds/unfolds all).
* Adding 'zi' Vim command support (toggle all folds).
* Adding 'zc' Vim command to close 1 level of folding at the current insertion cursor.
* Adding 'zC' Vim command to close all levels of folding at the current insertion cursor.
* Adding 'zo' Vim command to open 1 level of folding at the current insertion cursor.
* Adding 'zO' Vim command to open all levels of folding at the current insertion cursor.
* Adding 'zE' Vim command to delete all folds in the current editor.


